    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Londinio </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> <abbr>Vital</abbr> <abbr>Ad</abbr> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Rufus Callisuni salutem Epillico et omni<lb break="no" n="2"/>bus contubernalibus certiores vos esse <lb n="3"/>credo me recte valere si vos invi<lb break="no" n="4"/>cem fecistis rogo mittite omnia <lb n="5"/>diligenter cura agas ut illam puel<lb break="no" n="6"/>lam ad nummum redigas
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Privatbrief. (B): in Z. 3-4 indi/cem statt invi/cem.</p>
            </div>
